{"tid":85401,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"世界各地漢堡包雜錦","createTime":"2017-01-18T09:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T07:37:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cc6b835f37dd603c2a91753d7c8378ad125d7e7","tid":85401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OHdqvps.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOHdqvps.jpg&h=5e543bd6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n德國漢堡扒，無包，用薯仔代替<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5TETlzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5TETlzQ.jpg&h=221f07bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n墨西哥漢堡，跟美國最似，同樣會用大量肉同芝士<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fOsXhCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfOsXhCF.jpg&h=26b21f62&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n澳洲﹑紐西蘭用較多果蔬類食材<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hfXjJ4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhfXjJ4g.jpg&h=2ad199ed&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東亞飯堡，中國﹑越南﹑日本都有做過"},{"pid":"143251a63a176408d581b8f7ead10b2ba1df41a0","tid":85401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/03eq71i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F03eq71i.jpg&h=71dde514&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n印度漢堡，通常都係以雞肉或者菜做主打，有機會用綠咖哩調味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xdSuJU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxdSuJU3.jpg&h=fad7ec12&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n丹麥漢堡，牛肉食落個質感比較raw，多數會用茄汁﹑法汁同洋蔥汁調味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nUK2wLt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnUK2wLt.jpg&h=f5190e5a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n塞爾維亞多數原件上，食得比較粗豪，不過近年都開始有夾包既漢堡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/45oy1yX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F45oy1yX.jpg&h=b9533e4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n中國驢肉漢堡，亦叫驢肉燒餅，係十分傳統既一道中式小食"},{"pid":"6cc5f6529da14a5d7e645f7309401d60686171a0","tid":85401,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HrKuq7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHrKuq7n.jpg&h=63527c59&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n日本成日整埋D古古怪怪既漢堡，包括上面呢款朱古力醬漢堡...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/G16mwpt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FG16mwpt.jpg&h=c1c7a334&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n巴基斯坦既快餐業十分豐盛，呢類沙米烤肉漢堡幾乎係日常必食之一<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kVRamvs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkVRamvs.jpg&h=3dcb32c5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n加拿大熱漢堡分量十足，為偏冷地區既人提供足夠熱量"},{"pid":"078774893e6e6e992685cf7fb631eba523f07bb5","tid":85401,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:00:34.000Z","msg":"香港代表<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sopitas.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Fail-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sopitas.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2FFail-23.png&h=d0e78a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"590090eaa52d658e888435cbae7e596c022db9a2","tid":85401,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港代表<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sopitas.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Fail-23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sopitas.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F02%2FFail-23.png&h=d0e78a64&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾狗食"},{"pid":"db230077182a640532a1fa40550280ab8b538525","tid":85401,"uid":21